general_info:
Sara Construction LLC, builds new houses, and anything from remodeling to renovations. 
Experience is key in the construction business. After 35 years, our business has gained a reputation of using the finest craftsmanship in our building, and cutting no corners. 
Our prices are always competitive; We will beat any of our competitors’ estimates, and our jobs are always performed in a timely fashion. We specialize in both old and new houses, as well as commercial construction. 
 
Fully Insured 
We will BEAT any Competitors Estimate!!!!! 
SERVING NY, NJ, CT & PA 
$90 Sq. Ft.
